%% Trace: features/06-App生物辨識登入.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as AppMobile
    participant OS as DeviceBiometricAPI
    participant Ctrl as BiometricController
    participant Svc as BiometricLoginService
    participant Repo as BiometricDeviceTokenRepository
    participant JwtIssuer as JwtTokenService

    User->>App: 開啟 App
    App->>App: 偵測本機已啟用生物辨識
    App->>OS: 提示生物辨識 (BR-60)
    OS-->>App: 通過
    App->>OS: 取出加密儲存之 refresh_token
    OS-->>App: refresh_token
    App->>Ctrl: POST /biometric/login (refresh_token, device_id)
    Ctrl->>Svc: login(refresh_token, device_id)
    Svc->>Repo: findActiveByDeviceAndHash(device_id, refresh_token_hash, is_revoked=false)
    Repo-->>Svc: token row OR null
    alt token 有效
        Svc->>JwtIssuer: issue(subject=member_auth_id)
        JwtIssuer-->>Svc: access_token
        Svc-->>Ctrl: SessionToken
        Ctrl-->>App: 200 {access_token}
        App-->>User: 進入會員中心
    else token 已撤銷 (BR-62 / CLARIFY-06)
        Svc-->>Ctrl: invalid
        Ctrl-->>App: 401 BIOMETRIC_TOKEN_INVALID
        App->>OS: 清除裝置 token
        App-->>User: 「請重新登入」+ 顯示登入頁
    end
